\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Your year of marriage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 1916.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 And your year and place of birth?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Well the year was 1897. And it was - I don't know the number, I think it was 149 which was Church Road Battersea them days. Which }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16605066\charrsid8157865 is}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865  know}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16605066\charrsid8157865 n}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865  as Battersea Church Road today see, they've reversed it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 How many years did you live in the house where you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Oh well that I can't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 You moved when you were quite young did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Yes, oh yes, we moved several times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Where did you go from Church Road?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 
Well I think it was Althorpe Grove. And that was in West - what - they call it Westbury Grove but it was Bridge Road West them days. Still in Battersea. Oh I haven't been out of }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6311901\charrsid8157865 Battersea}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 . Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 How long did you live in that house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Well that I don't remember 'cos I was quite a youngster. And then we went to - we moved back to Church Road Battersea again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 About how old were you then, do you know?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Well - about seven or eight I suppose.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 How long did you live in Church Road that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 
Oh for quite a long time there. Yes. Yes. Quite a long time. I knew me way all round that part of Battersea when - Johnny Burns and Shirley Benn used to have the meetings in Battersea }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6311901\charrsid8157865 Square}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 
, and give the speeches and I as a girl used to listen and - like children do today we were singing vote, vote, vote for Johnny Burns, kick old Benny out the door. 'Course I was only a girl naturally. And that - I remember
 that. Remember all the shops in Battersea Square too, I can tell you the names of the people.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Were you still living in Church Road?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6311901\charrsid8157865 U}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 ntil 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Oh no, no, I'd moved to Battersea High Street 'fore then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Did you stay at that one until you were married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Yes. What }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6311901\charrsid8157865 at }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 
Battersea High Street?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Church Road.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 No, no, we'd moved -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 How old were you when you moved?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 We moved to - I think about fourteen when I went to Battersea }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6311901\charrsid8157865 High}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865  Street and then I lived there - I lived with my mother and father and stayed there 'til thirty-five - for thirty five years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Do you remember why your family made these moves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Well it's just that my father liked a garden and - there was a nice a big garden in the high street and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 It wasn't to be nearer his work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Oh no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Just to get a bigger garden?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Liked a bit of garden, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 How many brothers and sisters did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Two brothers. One sister died at five. So - she was older than - older than me.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Could you give me the birth order of the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Me brother is the eldest. And the youngest, I've got a brother. He - he was the youngest.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 How many years were there between each of you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Well my brother's seventy-seven now, t
he eldest, and the other one's - fifty-two this year. No - he must be older - not fifty-two. Sixty-two. Yes, sixty-two.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Where did the girl who died come in birth spacing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Oh in between the elder brother and me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Do you know how old your father was when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 How old was he when he died?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Eighty-two.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 When was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Not - my mother died - 1944 and he died six years after her. '50.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Do you know where he came from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Yes. King Street, Battersea, and nobody knows it. It's Westbridge Road now. That was King Street Battersea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 What was his occupation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Well - one time he was - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6311901\charrsid8157865 horse keeper}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 . And then he got kicked with a horse that he gave that up and - he went and worked for the Ministry. His brother worked on it and got him a job there.
