\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 What - the next job I went to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Was there only you at the first one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Only me there, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 What was the next job you went to then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Well I used to go to Bond Street then, to dressmake. Started dressmaking.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 An apprentice?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Yes. Yes. And I used to - I got that you see 'cos I used to get four shillings a week there, and my tea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 How did you get this job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Well somebody recommended me that lived next door but two to me. She used to go and took me with her you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 What exactly did you have to do in this job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Well at first - for a twelve month you had run errands and things and then when you wasn't doing that you were witting d
own doing needlework and - learnt little titbits of how to put hooks and eyes on and - which were in used those days and - petersham bands and all that sort of thing you used to have to do those. No, well - it was band that you - if you had a skirt you se
e, you'd have a petersham made to put the skirt over the top and stitch it with - make it all - neat and tidy you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 What hours did you do on this job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Nine - nine in morning 'til }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16605066\charrsid8157865 half}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865  past seven at night. And I used to walk to Bond Street nigh
t and morning. I starred out - eight o'clock and get there by nine - five to nine. Hour. But if I used to get some coppers during the day - I went for an errand for any of the assistants or anybody they might give mea - a penny you see, which was a lot of
 money, and if I didn't want to walk home - I'd have a penny ride and help me along you see which you could get those days. The whole fare was only tuppence ha'penny them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Tuppence ha'penny would be quite a chunk out of your wages wouldn't it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 
Oh well, that's why you couldn't ride. No, as I say, if I had any money given to me I might - but then - we - I were only young, I could walk I didn't mind, I was used to walking.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Was it quite common for people to walk long distances to work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Oh yes, yes, friends used to walk. We used to walk together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Did you have to work Saturdays there or Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Did you have any half days or holidays with pay? How long did you work there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Couple of years I think I was there. And
 I left there and went - went to work in Sloane Street, which was nearer home and I got more money. 'Cos I improved myself you see and - as you went up them days you got a bit more - money so of course it was nearer home and more money.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 But it was still dressmaking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Dressmaking, oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 How did you feel about your employers in the dressmaking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 All right, I got on very well there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Did you like the work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Yes. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16605066\charrsid8157865 But}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 
 the war broke out then you see. And - I got a job nearer home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 What did you do then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Machining.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 That's still dressmaking is it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 No. No. Bags. More money again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 What sort of bags were these?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Ordinary sacks. Sack stitching.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 How}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16605066\charrsid8157865  long}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 
 did you work on this job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Quite a while. See - about - three years I think it was.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 What were the hours on this job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Eight o'clock. Eight o'clock 'til - five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Was this Saturdays or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Did you have any holidays with pay on this job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Do you know how long they were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 No. Can't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Was it a week's holiday or was it job a Bank Holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 No, a week's holiday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 What were you paid?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 I don't remember. It's some time ago now you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Did you feel that in your different jobs that the wages were fair or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Well - of course in those days that's all there was to be got, whatever sort of job you went in for you didn't get much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Do you remember feeling at the time that it was a fair wage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Well - we - we were tr
aining so we just - accepted it. That's why you used to go from one job to another 'cos soon as you heard you got a bit more money somewhere else off you went to get that little bit more.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 What did you feel about your employers in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 All right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 They treated you quite well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 What jobs have you done since the first world war?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Well I've been down at - I was at Morgan's for twenty-three - twenty-three - I done two years in the first world war down there. And
 then there was a break in between when my husband come back from the war, I used to do little morning jobs. 'Cos I'd got one child, and she was six and a half I had another one. And then I used to do little morning jobs you see cos I was living with my m
other then and she would mind the baby while I went for a morning job. 'cos my husband was back from the war you see and he was back at work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 So when did you first stop }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16605066\charrsid8157865 working}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865  full time, what year would this be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Well - about 1919. And then I had a break - doing morning work you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Was this domestic work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 
Yes. Yes. When my husband came home from the war - I had a break and done this morning - little morning jobs and then - when this last war broke out 'course he didn't go, I got a full time job. I went back again - no, to Morgan's. Morgan's }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10516930\charrsid8157865 Crucible}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865  works.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 What do they do, what did you do there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 I - well in the first world war I done - two years down there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 You went from the sack factory to Morgan's?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 To Morgan's. One factory next door.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 What did you do in that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 
Oh - I was in the stores, serving. Of course, the two men in the stores went to the - war you see. And there was two of - us ladies took the - job over. But there was other - there was about - two - there was three men and a boy also besides us two women.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 What do Morgan's do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 
Oh - what do Morgan's do? You want to read their books today and see what they do. They're all over the world now. Make melting pots and carbons and everything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 You went back there in the second world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 1917 I went back there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 And you worked there until 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 And then you had these morning jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Jobs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 And then you went back to Morgan's again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Back in this war. So I had a long lapse -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Was that 1939?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 I had a lapse in between - big lapse in between you see, 'cos I didn't want all day work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Did you go back immediately the war started?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 No, not immediately - 'cos they told me then when I first wen
t I was too old. But of course as the war went on I wasn't too old. And then I stopped there 'til I was - sixty - I was sixty-seven at the Christmas and I went back for six weeks after that. So I was there six weeks in 1968. Was it, no, wait a minute. No,
 I've been left longer than that. '68. It's only '71 now isn't it. I'm getting mixed up. Must have been '66. Yes. Yes, 'cos it's longer than that. (1964)
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Would you have preferred any other type of occupation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 No, I liked the job in the stores. In the first world war.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Did you belong to any }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10516930\charrsid8157865 trade union}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865  or professional organisation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Yes, I did at one time.;
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Could you tell me when this was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Well it was in the latter part because Morgan's wasn't a trade union firm them day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 It was in the second world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6700382 HK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 War.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6491565 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5312448\charrsid8157865 Did you feel that employers and workers had the same interests or different?
